00:00:00.690 --> 00:00:03.770
Are you suffering from pain? If so, come into Pain Away and speak to one of our

00:00:03.770 --> 00:00:09.413
pain specialists. We can tailor a pain reduction plan just for you. Because we

00:00:09.413 --> 00:00:15.015
know that pain is personal. Pain is also complex, it's sensory, it's physical,

00:00:15.015 --> 00:00:20.954
it's emotional. For instance, for physical pain there are nerve cells. In your

00:00:20.954 --> 00:00:25.888
skin, called nociceptors, and these send signals of pain to your brain. For

00:00:25.888 --> 00:00:29.472
emotional pain, such as social rejection and bullying, the same areas of the

00:00:29.472 --> 00:00:34.760
brain are activated as in physical pain. And because we understand this, we can

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:39.620
tailor our pain reduction plan just for you. Pain Away. For your unique pain.

